Devoted Spirit (Counter)
Level: Crusader 7, Saint 7
Prerequisite: Two Devoted Spirit maneuvers
Initiation Action: 1 immediate action
Range: Melee attack
Target: One creature

As an immediate action, you can attempt a shield bash against an opponent you threaten.  You must have a shield equipped in order to initiate this maneuver.  This attack is made with a -2 penalty. If your shield attack hits, your target's next attack automatically misses. You use this maneuver before an opponent makes an attack.
